ratio
comparison of two quantities

equivalent ratio
ratio that have same quotient

ratio table
table listing pair of number that form equivalent ratio

how to calculate ratio
divide numerator / denominator

fraction notation
x / y

part to whole ratio
add numerator + denominator then divide each / sum; quotient equal part to whole

rate
comparison of two quantities measured in different unit

unit rate
rate in which second quantity in comparison equal one unit

how to calculate unit rate
divide first quantity / second quantity

how to calculate dollar rate
divide dollar amount / quantity
